snippet.title: AMBER HEARD Threw 'Haymaker' Punch At JOHNNY DEPP
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has stated that his ex wife Amber Heard threw a haymaker punch at him for reading in bed!!

First Heard left feces in their bed and now Amber Heard has thrown a haymaker punch at Johnny Depp.

Actor Johnny Depp has said his ex-wife Amber Heard’s allegations of domestic violence “mirrored” what he claims was her abuse towards him.

The Pirates Of The Caribbean star told the high court in London that “it seemed like everything she would accuse me of was something she had done to me”.

Depp (57) also accused Heard (34) of throwing a “haymaker” punch at him during a row after her 30th birthday party, hours after he had learned during a “bad” business meeting that he had lost $650 million (about €570 million).

The Hollywood actor made the claims on Monday during his fifth day of evidence in his libel action against the Sun newspaper.
